'''Titan Magazines''', also known as '''Titan Comics''', is the world's leading publisher of officially licensed film and television magazines. The company has published ''[[Star Wars Comic|Star Wars Comic UK]]'', [[Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine|''Star Wars: The Clone Wars'' Magazine]] (both edited by [[Jon Chapple]]), [[Star Wars Magazine (2014)|''Star Wars'' Magazine]], and [[Star Wars Rebels Magazine|''Star Wars Rebels'' Magazine]]. It also published ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'' until it began publishing ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' (edited by [[Jonathan Wilkins]] through [[Star Wars Insider 174|issue 174]]) during [[Celebration IV]] in May [[2007]].

